data.description: RV Parking and Boat Parking behind your fence.  With tall steel cover.  - No HOA - Space galore for all your toys. Huge driveway for extra vehicles. All these in the City!!!  Beautiful neighborhood, near everything.  Gorgeous updated kitchen with granite and very nice appliances. Home is spacious 3 bed, 2 and a half baths.  It also has an extra living area with closets, and bathroom nearby, which can be for a Mother in Law.  or an extra living area.  Lots of space!!! Very well kept home. With a new heat and air. Huge backyard with gorgeous immaculate pool. Must come and see before it is gone!  Hard to find a home with all these parking and space for all your fun toys and hobbies.
